                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d242">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Ehrman</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Panama</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 8, 1903</hi>.</date>
                        <lb/>(Received 11.23 p.m.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>It is reported that Colombian authorities have detained English steamers <hi
                        rend="italic">Manavi</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi> at Buenaventura.
                    Supposed to be to bring troops to the Isthmus.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Ehrman.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
